{"tid":683172,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"【Road to Ultra 2018 香港站】集中討論區","createTime":"2018-05-29T13:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T11:42:18.000Z","uid":178021,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fbe87dce4fec186a97240e528b57efc9473a1a75","tid":683172,"uid":178021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:01:29.000Z","msg":"仲有個零禮拜就係，點解仲未有人開post講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇人中意edm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n來自邁阿密的電音盛典香港 Road to Ultra 將於 <span style=\"color: red;\">2018 年 6 月 9 日（週六）</span>第三度旋風過境，吹襲香港！千呼萬喚的 RTU 熱帶氣旋於今年首次登陸亞洲國際博覽館，擺脫炙熱天氣高温限制，勢必刷新您的電子音樂節體驗。延續往年備受高度讚揚的國際級水平製作，加上今年獨有的室內場地優勢，聲與光的呈現將達極緻，嶄新的多元感觀視覺體驗配以神級電音藝人演出陣容，不能錯過年度香港電音節！ <br />\n<br />\n今年d line up，大家點睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/31886615_1647302602054781_6224927978787176448_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=9f89b1428a1ba86a005178295b3a06c0&amp;oe=5BC297D2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F31886615_1647302602054781_6224927978787176448_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D9f89b1428a1ba86a005178295b3a06c0%26oe%3D5BC297D2&h=daf1f6e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打買左飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊討論下"},{"pid":"494d03dac7e947fd8cb8398f4b0b9a4d8659fd57","tid":683172,"uid":178021,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:22:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qMbsHnsRo_E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqMbsHnsRo_E&d=YPAu4AnCEAaVi65pa0N96U%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=4aa3ecaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qMbsHnsRo_E</a><br />\n<br />\n條片已經睇到我好high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b65e6514b593df9b249439a3c63b3ea7a8e9ecd","tid":683172,"uid":10774,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-